    "After the intervention, N2 sleep time substantially increased, demonstrated with a scatterplot of the N2 sleep time in the elderly, but the sleep time was significantly increased.",
    "N3 sleep time experienced a small decline in the elderly, and deep sleep time was more aggregated, while REM sleep time increased.",
    "The waking time of the experimental group significantly increased after the intervention (p < 0.05), and there was no significant difference in other indicators throughout the intervention (p > 0.05) (Table 4).",
